components.text: [size=21][b][color=#000000] Maverick Buying: Where do we spot process patterns that imply procurement without involvement of the purchasing department?[/color][/b][/size]

[size=15][b][color=#000000] The involvement of a dedicated purchasing department for purchase orders leads to significant savings through optimized purchasing terms, applicable discounts and higher standardization.[/color][/b][/size]

[size=15][b][color=#000000] Financial impact = Maverick buying purchase order volume (<%=Currency%>) * discount potential when purchasing department included (%) * realization potential (%) * time factor (x)[/color][/b][/size]
[b][size=15] Net value of items involved in maverick buying (<%=Currency%>) - P2P[/size][/b]
[size=15] Time factor (scaling factor for a full 1 year period)[/size]

meta.expressionLhs: ROUND_MONTH ( PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Order Item' ) ) AS "#{Time}" FORMAT "%Y-%m"

buttons.variableValue: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1500 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.500 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 5000 THEN 'd) 1.500 - 5.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 5000 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 5.000 - 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  ELSE 'e) > 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>' END
